    <Relationships>
      <Refines>HL-PLAN-1.1</Refines>
      <Refines>HL-HARDWARE-2.3</Refines>
    </Relationships>
    <Content>
      The system shall define the cost of a path as the sum of the costs of its edges, where each edge cost is proportional to the distance between cell centers and may include additional penalties for turns or speed limitations.
